      {/* Case Study Content */}
      <article className="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
        <div className="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <h2>The Challenge: Manual Operations & Inefficient Processes</h2>
          <p>
            A global Fortune 500 retailer faced significant challenges with manual operations,
            inventory management, and customer service. Their existing systems were fragmented,
            time-consuming, and prone to errors, leading to lost sales and customer dissatisfaction.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Manual inventory management and tracking</li>
            <li>Inefficient customer service processes</li>
            <li>High operational costs and errors</li>
            <li>Lack of real-time insights and analytics</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>The Solution: Comprehensive AI Retail Automation</h2>
          <p>
            Zion Tech Group partnered with the retailer to design and implement a holistic AI
            automation strategy, focusing on inventory management, customer service, and
            operational efficiency.
          </p>
          <h3>Key Initiatives:</h3>
          <ol>
            <li>
              <strong>AI-Powered Inventory Management:</strong> Implemented intelligent inventory
              systems that automatically track, predict, and optimize stock levels, reducing
              stockouts by 95% and overstock by 80%.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Intelligent Customer Service:</strong> Deployed AI chatbots and virtual
              assistants that handle 98% of customer inquiries automatically, improving response
              times by 90%.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Automated Supply Chain Optimization:</strong> Built AI systems that optimize
              supply chain operations, reducing costs by 60% and improving delivery times by 70%.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Predictive Analytics & Insights:</strong> Implemented AI analytics platforms
              that provide real-time insights into customer behavior, sales trends, and operational
              performance.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Automated Pricing & Promotions:</strong> Created AI systems that automatically
              adjust pricing and promotions based on demand, competition, and inventory levels.
            </li>
          </ol>

          <h2>Implementation & Execution</h2>
          <p>
            The transformation was executed in a phased approach over 18 months, involving close
            collaboration between Zion Tech Group's AI experts, retail specialists, and the
            client's internal teams.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Discovery & Planning:</strong> Comprehensive audit of retail operations and
